description: Right in the heart of Texas, it's Austin Gelato! This Italian frozen treat is sweet to eat and great when you want to beat the heat! Austin Gelato is passionate about their gelato, making it in small batches from all-natural ingredients that are organic and locally sourced whenever possible. Offerings include hand-scooped cups, 4.2-liter pans or gelato bars dipped in dark Belgian chocolate as well as dairy-free sorbetto bars. Austin Gelato's freezer cart is a festive way to serve and makes any occasion a party. Whatever your sweet tooth craves, it's sure to love Austin Gelato!
name: Austin Gelato Company
